{{Quote|Sir, we are aboard a corvette-analog picket boat, length one hundred twenty-two meters, estimated crew ninety-eight.|YVH 2-1S|<ref name="The New Jedi Order: Star by Star">''[[The New Jedi Order: Star by Star]]''</ref>}}
'''''Exquisite Death''''' was a [[Yuuzhan Vong]] [[I'Friil Ma-Nat|corvette analog]] under the command of [[Commander/Legends|Commander]] [[Duman Yaght]] during the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]] in [[27 ABY/Legends|27 ABY]]. It was two decks tall and 122 meters long, with a crew of 98. It had a forward-facing bridge, three aft holds, and four main access corridors.

Duman received seventeen [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] captives from [[Lando Calrissian/Legends|Fitzgibbon Lane]], who was in truth [[Lando Calrissian/Legends|Lando Calrissian]], in the plan to deliever a team of Jedi Knights to [[Myrkr/Legends|Myrkr]] for the [[Mission to Myrkr]]. Once the vessal had crossed Yuuzhan Vong lines, the Jedi attacked and killed all of the Yuuzhan Vong and [[voxyn]] aboard, commandeering the ship for the rest of the journey. During the approach to Myrkr, Jedi Apprentice [[Ulaha Kore]] stayed aboard the ''Death'' to distract enemy forces so that her friends could sneak onto the [[Koros-Strohna|worldship]] ''[[Baanu Rass]]''. The ''Death'' and Kore were destroyed in the battle that followed.

